  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>\"シシテナオ-Even in Death-\"</strong> is a high-difficulty stealth horror action game that demands trial and error.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>■</strong>Recommended for players</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is perfect for those who want to enjoy tension through careful stealth gameplay.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>■Story</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is the story of a young girl who wakes up in a bizarre and unsettling world, where eerie creatures known as <strong>\"Ochibito\"</strong> roam.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132770/extras/150a802a521092359e8b735e699d3020.poster.avif?t=1743152505\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132770/extras/150a802a521092359e8b735e699d3020.webm?t=1743152505\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132770/extras/150a802a521092359e8b735e699d3020.mp4?t=1743152505\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>■Stealth Action</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>\"SHI SHI TE NA O-Even in Death-\"</strong> is an action game that demands perfect stealth. As eerie creatures known as \"Ochibito\" roam, you must suppress your footsteps, crouch to hide, and move while holding your breath. Understanding the characteristics of the Ochibito and carefully observing their movements is key to surviving.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132770/extras/9dd542030d88f55307f7aa8ab0ebf114.poster.avif?t=1743152505\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132770/extras/9dd542030d88f55307f7aa8ab0ebf114.webm?t=1743152505\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132770/extras/9dd542030d88f55307f7aa8ab0ebf114.mp4?t=1743152505\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132770/extras/96c96be5dfe2c2311bb60f33adeccfc1.avif?t=1743152505\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132770/extras_big/96c96be5dfe2c2311bb60f33adeccfc1.avif?t=1743152505 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>■World</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game's 2D backgrounds, terrifying creatures that scurry around, enemies that suddenly appear from behind, and eerie voices and sound effects combine to create an unstable atmosphere that constantly keeps the player on edge.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132770/extras/ae0369d660f5a02fc7bd1a1dc4817127.poster.avif?t=1743152505\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132770/extras/ae0369d660f5a02fc7bd1a1dc4817127.webm?t=1743152505\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132770/extras/ae0369d660f5a02fc7bd1a1dc4817127.mp4?t=1743152505\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132770/extras/7792cc6709521b4d20cab7c641fde965.avif?t=1743152505\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132770/extras_big/7792cc6709521b4d20cab7c641fde965.avif?t=1743152505 width=800 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132770/extras/d7eb3b2926deef0113537c798b6d2300.avif?t=1743152505\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132770/extras_big/d7eb3b2926deef0113537c798b6d2300.avif?t=1743152505 width=800 height=448 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・It is strongly recommended to play with headphones to accurately gauge enemy positions and actions through sound. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is developed in Full HD. When played in fullscreen on a monitor with a resolution higher than Full HD, jagged edges (aliasing) may appear on the screen.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It was created using Pixel Game Maker MV.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>If the game does not start</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Installing the trial version of Pixel Game Maker MV on Steam may provide the necessary DLL files for your computer, allowing the game to run.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>\"シシテナオ-Even in Death-\"</strong> is a high-difficulty stealth horror action game that demands trial and error.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>■</strong>Recommended for players</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is perfect for those who want to enjoy tension through careful stealth gameplay.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>■Story</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is the story of a young girl who wakes up in a bizarre and unsettling world, where eerie creatures known as <strong>\"Ochibito\"</strong> roam.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132770/extras/150a802a521092359e8b735e699d3020.poster.avif?t=1743152505\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132770/extras/150a802a521092359e8b735e699d3020.webm?t=1743152505\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132770/extras/150a802a521092359e8b735e699d3020.mp4?t=1743152505\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>■Stealth Action</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>\"SHI SHI TE NA O-Even in Death-\"</strong> is an action game that demands perfect stealth. As eerie creatures known as \"Ochibito\" roam, you must suppress your footsteps, crouch to hide, and move while holding your breath. Understanding the characteristics of the Ochibito and carefully observing their movements is key to surviving.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132770/extras/9dd542030d88f55307f7aa8ab0ebf114.poster.avif?t=1743152505\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132770/extras/9dd542030d88f55307f7aa8ab0ebf114.webm?t=1743152505\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132770/extras/9dd542030d88f55307f7aa8ab0ebf114.mp4?t=1743152505\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132770/extras/96c96be5dfe2c2311bb60f33adeccfc1.avif?t=1743152505\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132770/extras_big/96c96be5dfe2c2311bb60f33adeccfc1.avif?t=1743152505 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>■World</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game's 2D backgrounds, terrifying creatures that scurry around, enemies that suddenly appear from behind, and eerie voices and sound effects combine to create an unstable atmosphere that constantly keeps the player on edge.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132770/extras/ae0369d660f5a02fc7bd1a1dc4817127.poster.avif?t=1743152505\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132770/extras/ae0369d660f5a02fc7bd1a1dc4817127.webm?t=1743152505\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132770/extras/ae0369d660f5a02fc7bd1a1dc4817127.mp4?t=1743152505\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132770/extras/7792cc6709521b4d20cab7c641fde965.avif?t=1743152505\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132770/extras_big/7792cc6709521b4d20cab7c641fde965.avif?t=1743152505 width=800 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132770/extras/d7eb3b2926deef0113537c798b6d2300.avif?t=1743152505\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132770/extras_big/d7eb3b2926deef0113537c798b6d2300.avif?t=1743152505 width=800 height=448 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・It is strongly recommended to play with headphones to accurately gauge enemy positions and actions through sound. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is developed in Full HD. When played in fullscreen on a monitor with a resolution higher than Full HD, jagged edges (aliasing) may appear on the screen.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It was created using Pixel Game Maker MV.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>If the game does not start</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Installing the trial version of Pixel Game Maker MV on Steam may provide the necessary DLL files for your computer, allowing the game to run.</p>",
